{"tid":1133737,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]原來izone珉周吹蕭咁叻...[內有吹簫圖]","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T12:02:42.000Z","uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3da0484d6d54118201d5615a318459a1b278d85a","tid":1133737,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/img/bao/uploaded/i4/i4/276497075/TB2Gbe1aigSXeFjy0FcXXahAXXa_!!276497075.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fbao%2Fuploaded%2Fi4%2Fi4%2F276497075%2FTB2Gbe1aigSXeFjy0FcXXahAXXa_%21%21276497075.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg&h=4f683275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/img/bao/uploaded/i4/i2/2816303977/TB2weU4akUkyKJjy1zjXXX1wFXa_!!2816303977.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fbao%2Fuploaded%2Fi4%2Fi2%2F2816303977%2FTB2weU4akUkyKJjy1zjXXX1wFXa_%21%212816303977.jpg_196x196Q50s50.jpg&h=5cb59923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ax/api/res/1.2/deiprKWpYud1QN1I2t4C5Q--~D/Zmk9aW5zZXQ7dz0zMDA7aD0zMDA7O2FwcGlkPW1zdG9yZXM-/https://s.yimg.com/ut/api/res/1.2/AbNx7KIo.boHeFNJXTri0w--~B/YXBwaWQ9eXR3bWFsbDtjYz0zMTUzNjAwMDtoPTYwMDtxPTgxO3c9NjAw/https://s.yimg.com/fy/3b80/item/p0349132591742-item-0d19xf4x0436x0423-m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fax%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdeiprKWpYud1QN1I2t4C5Q--~D%2FZmk9aW5zZXQ7dz0zMDA7aD0zMDA7O2FwcGlkPW1zdG9yZXM-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fut%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAbNx7KIo.boHeFNJXTri0w--~B%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3bWFsbDtjYz0zMTUzNjAwMDtoPTYwMDtxPTgxO3c9NjAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Ffy%2F3b80%2Fitem%2Fp0349132591742-item-0d19xf4x0436x0423-m.jpg&h=2edca2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簫又稱洞簫，是中國古老的吹管樂器，特徵為單管、豎吹、開管、邊稜音發聲。「簫」字在唐代以前本指排簫，唐宋以來，由於單管豎吹的簫日漸流行，便稱編管簫爲排簫，以示區別。至於「洞簫」之名，則來自於簫管底端之開孔。 其音色圓潤輕柔，幽靜典雅，常用於獨奏、琴簫合奏或絲竹樂演奏。<br />\n漢代以前，無論是橫吹還是豎吹的管樂器，都可稱為笛，從馬融《長笛賦》可知，豎吹之笛原有四孔，皆在前側，而後西漢京房多加一背孔，此型制已與今傳之洞簫基本上一致。漢代王褒曾作《洞簫賦》，然而文中有「參差」一詞，故應是指排簫。<br />\n笛曲的最早記錄見於晉書, 但只說「三弄」卻並未記錄曲名，此曲之譜已不存在，僅存有據此改編而來的古琴曲梅花三弄。<br />\n唐代，開始以「笛」專稱橫吹之笛，至於豎吹之簫，則因其長度為一尺八寸，稱之為「尺八」，並傳到日本成為「古尺八」。而「簫」在唐代以前則是用來稱排簫。<br />\n元代，宴樂之器已有五孔簫的記載，也將簫與排簫做了區別。簫在之後的宮廷禮樂都有廣泛的應用。<br />\n明代，單管直吹的「簫」、多管的「排簫」、橫吹的「笛」有了更明顯的區別。現存最早的獨立譜見於《文林聚寳萬卷星羅》，為工尺譜。清代有任兆麟的《簫譜》一書。<br />\n到二十世紀，彭祉卿於《今虞琴刊》發表〈新制雅簫圖說〉，發明8孔雅簫，又名琴簫，便於與琴音合奏，現在的八孔簫是據此發展得來，強調其十二平均律便於樂器合奏。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd1caf5289c0d5d13c7541e03ea0e237d00dd2e","tid":1133737,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"唔好逼我反降."},{"pid":"065d68779d445994b3fdabb242ab83aa431e6258","tid":1133737,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"仲以為賓狗開post添"},{"pid":"1de53a9825eb84db5479784d45ccd292c89cdd45","tid":1133737,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fd1caf5289c0d5d13c7541e03ea0e237d00dd2e","tid":1133737,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"唔好逼我反降."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"有事慢慢傾"},{"pid":"e7e65a80d99e5d291c0dafba93157cadc2ca1ef1","tid":1133737,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾開垃圾POST"},{"pid":"e7dddae63ec316d262aae2786c059eae3eb7c3f3","tid":1133737,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7e65a80d99e5d291c0dafba93157cadc2ca1ef1","tid":1133737,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾開垃圾POST"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"非"},{"pid":"fee92cff7f49105a71886bd1c0e08b4b1c6aa055","tid":1133737,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"影撚衰牙降 屌樓主老母"},{"pid":"77ddfc95aac1918c39d4d6b8